Sometimes the items or devices we have can be lifesaving. In the event of an emergency many things are useful even if they have never had a use before. Someone materialistic who holds on to all of the dear items will have a greater odds of survival than someone who criticizes others for being materialistic. The person who is materialstic will have access to the items they have hoarded or saved up over time, even if it is something random such as a wall hanging sword while the person whom is a criticizer will be left defenseless and in peril.
